videos.headline: Franks finds Burks for early Arkansas TD
videos.description: Feleipe Franks rolls to his left and throws a dime to Treylon Burks to give Arkansas the early 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Franks finds Burks for early Arkansas TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia and Arkansas each get an INT on back-to-back possessions
videos.description: Georgia's Richard LeCounte picks off Feleipe Franks, then a few plays later Arkansas' Montaric Brown gets the interception against D'Wan Mathis.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia and Arkansas each get an INT on back-to-back possessions) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pickens catches, turns and dives for 6
videos.description: George Pickens scores the first touchdown of the season for Georgia and puts the Bulldogs in the lead over Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pickens catches, turns and dives for 6) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pick-6 for UGA, Dawgs pulling away
videos.description: Eric Stokes gets in front of a pass for an interception and takes it back to the house for a UGA touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pick-6 for UGA, Dawgs pulling away) 2020/09/26 ESHEET
